      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it tucked away in the garage, and never missed a service. It\u2019s spotless inside and out, drives like a total dream, and you\u2019ll be hard-pressed to find another one this clean. Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
