      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a masterclass in mechanical harmony, powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six featuring six individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system. The chassis remains factory-spec with zero subframe fatigue, and the Getrag 6-speed manual provides precise, short-throw engagement. Finished in concours-grade paint with a pristine cabin, this example retains its original suspension geometry and limited-slip differential integrity, offering the visceral feedback and linear power delivery that defined an era of German engineering.",
