    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in absolute showroom condition since the day it left the dealership. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections\u2014no rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. It has been exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed, preserving the integrity of the paint and factory trim. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any sun damage or cracking. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the climate control, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having followed a strict maintenance schedule at authorized service centers with all records available for review. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule that provides the experience of buying brand new. Includes both original keys, the factory window sticker, and all original owner manuals.",
